            "title": "Population dynamics, reproduction, and diet of the lesser long-nosed bat (Leptonycteris curasoae) in Jalisco, Mexico: implications for conservation",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Kathryn E.",
                    "lastName": "Stoner"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
